item.description: Let's have a bonfire! Last week it was a blast. If you did not go last week it is at Sawyer Beach. Everyone is invited, not just volleyball players. You can meet us at Jenness State Beach. Please comment on what you plan to bring for food, paper goods or firewood. I will bring samores. Keilbasa, sausage, hot dogs, rolls, potato salad or pasta salad would be a good idea. (Don't forget ketchup) I have plenty of kindling, we just need plenty of firewood. Can't wait to see you there!
